  "instructions": [
    "In a bowl, mix chickpeas with avocado, red onion, tomatoes, green salsa, olive oil, lime juice, cumin, and salt. Stir well until combined.",
    "Divide the mixture evenly among the tortilla wraps. Top each wrap with a spoonful of the vegetable mixture.",
    "Heat the remaining olive oil in a non-stick pan over medium-high heat. Place a wrapped tortilla on the heated pan, cooking for about 2 minutes per side or until golden brown and warm.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro before serving."
